				<td colspan="2"><span>My first time trying this was when his pathing wasn't terribly good. I pulled it using mostly this method, but when I got to the other side, and waiting for him to surface, he never showed. I used bind sight to find out where he was and he was at his spawn point... 
<br />

<br />
Ok, no problem, got a bard to assist me to watch him with bind sight, tried again... nothing. 
<br />

<br />
In the end I had to walk him out, stay in lava till he made it through the cave have someone swim in lava to tag. Most difficult pull ever (DI helped allot since I couldn't leave lava, and soon as you see him, it's already too late) 
<br />

<br />
Now he's pretty easy to pull, just tag and run like a scared chicken. 
<br />

