				<td colspan="2"><span>I never used DA to pull.  The range on RoT is shorter then the range on the Bellow AA.  Maybe causing damages allows the possibility of being shadow stepped.  
<br />

<br />
The pita crutch of this pull is finding the tunnel right off.  Once finding the tunnel isn't a problem, then there isn't a problem.  Pulse Selo's (drum should already be equiped for resists), pulse PoV, pulse RoT, run like a little girl in terror.  With lev and drum modified selo's the only damage taken is from lava.  Just don't forget to restart PoV after hitting the lava so it doesn't drop during the run.
<br />

