				<td colspan="2"><span>I actualy loved the Quavonis pull when my guild was doing it.  The way i'd find the tunnel was stand in the dead center of the pool look straight down begin to circle (kinda drill like) and go down untill I hit the bottom.  Do a 360 and i'd usualy see the tunnel.  I'd usualy use DA on the return trip about halfway through the tunnel and wait for him to catch up with me then keep going as i've outdistanced him a few times pulling.
<br />

<br />
For weird pulls i've become a bit fan of DI actualy,  saves lives!  (Sometimes =/).  If you are getting comfortable with this pull i'd recommend DI as it will give you a bit of a buffer if you get low.  </span></td>
